{"Id":477,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-anonymousgroupo","Author":"Anonymous Group Of Translators","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"Goodword Books , http://www.goodwordbooks.com/ , Center for Peace and Spirituality , https://www.cpsglobal.org/","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以穹苍和启明星盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"你怎能知道启明星是什么"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"是那灿烂的明星。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"每个人都有一个保护者。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"教人思 想一下，他自己是用什么造成的"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他是射出的精液造成 的。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"那精液是从脊柱和肋骨之间发出的。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"真主确是能 448\t第八七章 至尊（艾尔拉） 使他复原的，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"那是在一切秘密被揭穿之日。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"他绝没 有能力，也没有援助者。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"以含雨的云"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"和有缝的地发 誓，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"这确是分别真伪的言辞，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"这不是笑话。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"他们 必定要用计谋，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"我也要用计谋。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"所以你当宽限不信 道的人们，你当宽限他们一下。§"}]}